Element


citerefentry
&citerefentry.purpose;


&citerefentry.synopsis.gen;
Description



This element is a citation to a RefEntry.  It must include
a RefEntryTitle that should exactly match the title of a 
RefEntry.


Processing expectations


This element implicitly links to the RefEntry with the
same RefEntryTitle (in the same volume, as defined by
ManVolNum).



&format.inline; Usually the ManVolNum is put in parentheses.




